---
title: BBQ Cheddar Beef Burgers with Crispy Shallots and Ranch-Dressed Salad
description: Nothing beats hunger like a juicy, stacked burger. Crushed crispy shallots and BBQ Seasoning are the secret ingredients in these succulent beef burgers that also feature gooey cheddar cheese nestled between two toasted artisan buns. Prepare to get a little messy!
